-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/blackrock-calls-for-global-etf-labeling-standards-audio-.html
 BlackRock Inc., the world's 
biggest provider of exchange-traded funds,  urged U.S. lawmakers
to bar products that rely on derivatives from being marketed as 
ETFs to avoid confusion with their traditional counterparts.  
Bloomberg Radio's Catherine Cowdery reports on Exchange Traded 
Funds.   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 01:54
 